ding dynamic access scenarios. Let's see what I find!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0db78ac3875b81430169f0098e7894819e846a6ce6bd96fefd\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp8AmgUsBtHdv5Pz1dWZVwvZVQE8o0HDwpzS6zEHxhJuKi7V1TcI6yUz8MkMy5beU1pDscKJRbcAj1b6MAe_iWP7G_QhbYxWSuxNvCXrfosKqvDEhulyrcuG4_38nHy8cKiED86huzNTy6LfBPAa6wyOKPI9en2HSDEytUJseND94fZRTa1B6nfrK8oTsyZawR0fVMhD_npY2ZG4RUOizIosPSC4QZIPbfVdjRQ8wJCx2scPh4Rt4LV9aY9YIdDQuITGYFy_u2KT4cfqFiNkkPouTwUn4kSwbs2HgUsJmowzDp_-udhjUY2S-pabLuxCrqxilI2j6XlgjS0s5cO8xCUQKYcugqkKt676Az1pAx7XYR5gjiLb04WHKnlaGDokNNyRL4Pw-_NsvE_Iw62Aw1hWBoX6B93s51_akNggsBhDmsMYhaxX3DuDVYFAgqlljkiudAxqbQKcFTkMTAaYAdChb5XXSwL_e93DG6H5CRQyrAkpgwtDNhyjklvCOtBVhBRJWu3S6xQlZ0ZINDGI20ghSxU1zz5a0Pe0L1aE7X9Qj3S3pZsISUhT6Ca8HwynKkbO3-Iv3beZJVymOjuvBcKIx1ZeMTJIs1XYv0wwx651_QZ7LabExJnOdoSogHCclQC4vOYtMsS1O0TEoQCAPAuTL0kThcVM33bHmg_S1wNBER4Lv_Lj6h8nRGZeYjoWGSZa-l6BILAmNuqahmywmtBm33RJ0XUrPNxA7qVZsE9grNXzdBBhn6TbU3LXkXxEtmAO7Gl3-7PeDvmo2oolwaEcFgiJWv-7ZWiClNglfTgpiUqizzxqNfzR0AnWhXVbNKwi_JoeUCn3YQY9GbtXFug6cbEyImjMp3Py5uK3b6vFiFiazSdaGP_pWffveWN5YHLhqqeP113kcZi8WBXR3CJzjZBsqhOZGH3pDEuBLlP7SJObklZ3Uy5TSoTFUW9W1YCEVpL1Z5u-wKsZOeB1cpsaxfIPqCf9RTa2Wggp4m06e01DPVZa29M-4bc8wnicw-_8xntgcAYq854Xxg28a6pLklD7XaiCUvoe_kfchQptxY9LpjIU842EqxQ0UBiaTJvHLW9MIDqHKUrFpMINGPb5JjO0pWOLH-3jCU5ZYv8_pq_VAzLgd0wKea_4YfORp9znWI5-j1jytS2IJT2k2FdTnknPZnYYKU3SieEN6L4TWQvVkz3mv8e1C9k_BmzWPwrvHlqwABm6vGGLeFoRGoiY0dWqxO2fQuXfPel3VANDx1hxfR8OOiMN1fkRGugZO8V2Lfi9hgJh-P8OFboLHfDccW_2_aoRD7ScgGoStVT711Zm_9DMex-pA6dPFAbYSWn2d-5R3xJX_myoAXr8JWi9mqxObKQzd6zuoQ53jR80FUZURL0RlriUMLvBRw9hsqVQIccepABqApD4gv4eJSaswO9EXqWxCBtlgnwV90XhkdKhYU2B1x91iJjjJd01cPxelWl6wJcMJv_3c07UZG1kW59ctSZ8l6x7_CwObpb4IwV0ckWEctk3PHeOneImoBYRR4WyJcJ62X40copXbai8hqacFtKYXx2NOYYrzX7iBL_e_GRuMqjYRjey3m6iSS67mDri_pgWTstuVO3vU76bb_ND6vxhSGYIu7j0NoVM3S9MIw67Wew78k5q6-YNhey2bNmFB9H8-dDgrTdPP1Afc6ZEcQGm9GRsdRvqlt4AZ9y2pdaaHu9mdKSCKRnl8zEN-g3hzxMfa_loaklkir3iGQCiU-QxPoDxXG6etFUC2XfkVtJ_ZAoXO-gjMDr0rXGd7X07YjK